# Cursor Project Rules

- Project must be modular and scalable.
- Use clearly named folders and follow Flutter best practices.
- Comments should be concise and only where logic is complex.
- Keep all rules in sync with tech-stack and architecture files.
- Firebase should be treated as the single source of truth.
- Riverpod must always be used with Riverpod Generator.
- go_router dependency must be used for navigation.